                Hic requiescit <lb n="2"/>Valentinus qui <lb n="3"/>vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXXVIII Mar<lb break="no" n="4"/>ontius pater Agri<lb break="no" n="5"/>cia co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iux</abbr></expan> et <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> ei<lb break="no" n="6"/>us t&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;tulum <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uerunt</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Kreuzes mit symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben.</p>
            </div>
